  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6, type: 3}
  m_Name: Aaryaveer_Lore
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GV.UI.CharacterLoreData
  characterName: Aaryaveer
  tagline: The crown of Nandana does not kneel.
  rarity: Epic
  role: Balanced Striker
  regionLabel: Kingdom
  regionName: Nandana
  factionLabel: Faction
  factionName: Devas
  powerClass: Supreme Astra Powers
  terrainMastery: Dual Terrain Mastery
  tharaResonance: Normal Thara Resonance
  backstory: "Crown prince of Nandana, the highest kingdom of the Devas. His father
    ruled unchallenged until Roudra \u2014 his most trusted general \u2014 turned the
    Asura forces of Daitya Giri against him. The king survived but the throne fractured,
    and the other kingdoms sensed weakness. Aaryaveer enters the Garuda Trials to reunify
    Nandana\u2019s shattered alliances and prove the Devas still hold supremacy over
    the Akasa Raajyas. He wields Supreme Astra \u2014 the highest tier of divine weaponry
    \u2014 but his Thara Resonance is only Normal, meaning he burns through power fast
    and must fight smart to outlast opponents with deeper reserves."
  strengths: "Versatile across all combat situations \u2014 no critical gap in his
    abilities\nSupreme Astra grants access to the most powerful weapon class among
    Sarathi\nNatural leader; Dual Terrain Mastery lets him fight effectively in any
    arena"
  weaknesses: "Normal Thara Resonance \u2014 burns power faster than Yakshas or Manavas
    pilots\nEmotionally compromised by Roudra\u2019s betrayal; hesitates against former
    allies\nSpreads his focus too thin trying to master everything rather than specializing"
  rivals: "Roudra \u2014 Asura warlord who broke his kingdom\nKaevik \u2014 QiNEXi
    arms dealer suspected of supplying Roudra\u2019s weapons tech"
